# ReBAC × Cedar (embedded) — document → folder → org-unit → ancestor-unit graph
# Membership at a parent company grants visibility into subsidiaries' documents.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### ALLOW — persona is member at the doc's org (or an ancestor org)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rebac",
  "principal": "psn-272633",
  "action": "doc.view",
  "resource_type": "RebacDocument",
  "resource": "rdoc-000072"
}

### DENY — persona from a different tenant (root org) — no relationship path
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rebac",
  "principal": "psn-357448",
  "action": "doc.view",
  "resource_type": "RebacDocument",
  "resource": "rdoc-000072"
}
